channel.title: How do i change my servers starting gear?
channel.description: I want to change it to dragon plate legs fire cape white phat desert boots and mime gloves...how?

item.title: How do i change my servers starting gear?
item.dc:creator: @OWNER_2007 OWNER 2007
item.description:
@OWNER_2007 wrote:

Step 1: Open up player.java

Step 2: Press Ctrl+F

Step 2: Search for " Giving the player an unique look "

Step 3: Change the items that are under it.

Step 4: Save, close, compile.
